	0.3.0 Release
	* Added multiple test units under test/ subdir in order to ensure
	  right working of combos making for bots.

	* Inhibit secondary mouse button for human player iff it is pressed
	  for ending the current round but this player does not have one combo
	  of four cards and the another one of three cards (or vice versa), or
	  a big stairway (seven cards). Rules are rules, for everyone!

